data.description: This property boasts an expansive and enchanting lot adorned with mature shade trees. Situated just under a mile away from the local cafe and outside the city limits. The renowned Clark Gardens and recreational trail are only a short drive away, while Garner Schools are conveniently located just half a mile from the property. Inside, the house features recently updated flooring, creating a fresh and inviting atmosphere. The spacious backyard provides ample space for entertaining guests. Parking is a breeze with three covered spaces available. Mineral Wells is an inviting community, currently undergoing the renovation of the iconic Baker Hotel. Close proximity to Mineral Wells State Park & Lake, Additionally, the area boasts excellent shopping, dining, and entertainment options. For a taste of history and charm, the historic Weatherford Downtown Square is less than 30 minutes away. Don't miss out on this remarkable property that combines comfort, convenience, and a desirable location.
